{
  "name": "ugc-factory",
  "version": "0.1.2",
  "description": "Interview-driven UGC video ad factory for Claude Code. Casts a fresh AI creator and product as Higgsfield Elements per ad (stateless, no saved avatar), generates ratio-matched keyframes, renders Seedance 2.0 clips, and stitches a finished short-form ad with ffmpeg.",
